text: @latimes @UROCKlive1 This is the progression of the coronavirus. Headache. Fever. Muscle aches. Extreme fatigue. Deep dry cough. Virus infects the lungs. Lungs begin to fill with fluid. Infectious pus. Increasingly difficult to breathe. Oxygen depletion. More fatigue. Struggling and gasping for air.
